      "comment": "BRINDLE BENNY (6) has been in the frame at his last two runs, most recently when second (19.85) in a Other over 342m at this track. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from the tricky draw. Likely to improve sharply this time. VICTA BOB (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (20.27) in a Other at this track. Can do much better this time. SEBON DISCO (8) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only a neck from Cool It Miss in second (23.09) at Gawler. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Will give a great sight again. DEEP PURPLE (4) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
